{"lemma":"مِرْفَقِ","slug":"مِرْفَقِ","root":"ر.ف.ق","root_slug":"ر-ف-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ف-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مِرْفَق","root":"رفق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":12},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n16212","n16213","n16214"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%81%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"elbow"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"device"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"device; crank"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"armrest"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"convenience, amenity","examples":[{"text":"يَنْشُرْ لَكُمْ رَبُّكُم مِن رَحْمَتِهِ وَيُهَيِّئْ لَكُم مِنْ أَمْرِكُم مِرْفَقًا","english":"Your Lord will reveal for you something of His mercy and prepare for you in your affair some comfort."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"appurtenance"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"civilizational institutions","tags":["in-plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"comfort","tags":["in-plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"public utilities","tags":["in-plural"],"examples":[{"text":"الْمَرَافِقُ ٱلْعَامَّةُ","english":"public utilities"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"installations","tags":["in-plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"facilities","tags":["in-plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"an attachment"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ر ف ق (r f q); tool noun in the sense of a thing used for ease and comfort; hence a thing used to relax upon, and devices providing convenience.\n\nNoun of place from the root ر ف ق (r f q)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n16212","headword_ar":"مَرْفَقٌ","root":"rfq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mirofaqN","text_ar":"مِرْفَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n16213","headword_ar":"مَرْفِقٌ","root":"rfq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows, in three places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n16214","headword_ar":"مِرْفَقٌ","root":"rfq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marofiqN","text_ar":"مَرْفِقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"inf. ns. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafaqa","text_ar":"رَفَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, O, K,) of which ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marofaqN","text_ar":"مَرْفَقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also is an inf. n. (O, K.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing by which one profits,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gains advantage"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"benefit."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K.) It is said in the Kur [xviii. 15],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wayuhay~iy^u lakumo mino A^amorikumo mirofaqFA","text_ar":"وَيُهَيِّيُ لَكُمْ مِنْ اَمْرِكُمْ مِرْفَقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marofiqFA","text_ar":"مَرْفِقًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to different readers, [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And He will prepare for you a condition of your case by which ye shall profit"},{"kind":"text","text":"], but no one reads ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marofaqFA","text_ar":"مَرْفَقًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) which, however, is allowable, meaning ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rifoqFA","text_ar":"رِفْقًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rifoqN","text_ar":"رِفْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence.]) The pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maraAfiqu","text_ar":"مَرَافِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b3-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maraAfiqu Ald~aAri","text_ar":"مَرَافِقُ الدَّارِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such appertenances"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conveniences"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the house as the privy and the kitchen and the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sinks, and the like, of the house:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) and particularly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"privies:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:) when used in these senses, the sing. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mirofaqN","text_ar":"مِرْفَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"only, with kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":"and fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"f","text_ar":"ف"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, Msb,) likened to the noun signifying an instrument. (Msb.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hay~izN","text_ar":"حَيِّزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hwz","text_ar":"حوز"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-  And from the same words in the sense expl. in the second sentence above, (Msb,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mirofaqN","text_ar":"مِرْفَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marofiqN","text_ar":"مَرْفِقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elbow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elbow-joint;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place where the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iraAE","text_ar":"ذِرَاع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"joins upon the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaDud","text_ar":"عَضُد"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K;) [in other words,] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place where the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaDud","text_ar":"عَضُد"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is connected with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAEid","text_ar":"سَاعِد"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Mgh;) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mrfq","text_ar":"مرفق"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a man:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) [and in like manner in a beast, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elbow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elbowjoint,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the JK, S, O, and K, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arofaqu","text_ar":"اَرْفَقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and in countless other instances: but in the K voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rukobapN","text_ar":"رُكْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(q. v.), it seems to be applied to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knee"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a beast:] pl. as above. (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["AZ","O","K","S","Mgh","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}